ds\n38:   - `store Store` тАФ for session state lookup\n39:   - `lifecycleManager *SandboxLifecycleManager` тАФ for sandbox deletion delegation\n40:   - `interval time.Duration` тАФ for cleanup check interval\n41:   - `idleTimeout time.Duration` тАФ for idle threshold\n42:   - `stopCh chan struct{}` тАФ for graceful shutdown signal\n43:   - `wg sync.WaitGroup` тАФ for goroutine synchronization\n44:   - `logger Logger` тАФ for structured logging\n45:   - `idleMu sync.RWMutex` тАФ protects `idleTimeout` for thread-safe access\n46:   - `lastCleanupTime time.Time` тАФ tracks last cleanup cycle\n47:   - `lastCleanupMu sync.RWMutex` тАФ protects `lastCleanupTime`\n48:   - File: `pkg/agentd/idle_cleanup.go`\n49:   - Verification: `go build ./pkg/agentd`\n50: \n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 345. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018 тАФ Agentd чй║щЧ▓ц╕ЕчРЖцОзхИ╢хЩи Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-018 тАФ Agentd чй║щЧ▓ц╕ЕчРЖцОзхИ╢хЩи |\n| Module | `pkg/agentd` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Design | [Stage ST-3 completed] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Core Types & Constants (ST-1)\n\n- [ ] **T1.1**: Create `pkg/agentd/doc.go` with package documentation\n  - Package name: `agentd`","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-018/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775865331519,"end":1775865331527}}}}
